title: Indochinese Leopard
author: OrangeConcrete
pages:
Indochinese Leopard
Fun Facts!

-------------------

1. The Indochinese
Leopard is a
medium-size big cat,
and adult males weigh
between 35-55 kg, and
females generally
weigh less. They can
get bigger or smaller
as well.  ----->

2. As with many other
animals in this zoo, it
is classified as an
endagered species,
due to deforestation,
illegal hunting, etc.

3. They are known for
their stealth and
agility, and are good
climbers.
